#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.10/site-packages/numpy/__init__.py:docstring
#: of numpy.dot:34
msgid ""
"Output argument. This must have the exact kind that would be returned if it "
"was not used. In particular, it must have the right type, must be C-"
"contiguous, and its dtype must be the dtype that would be returned for "
"`dot(a,b)`. This is a performance feature. Therefore, if these conditions "
"are not met, an exception is raised, instead of attempting to be flexible."
msgstr ""

