#: of numpy.dot:44
msgid ""
"Returns the dot product of `a` and `b`.  If `a` and `b` are both scalars or "
"both 1-D arrays then a scalar is returned; otherwise an array is returned. "
"If `out` is given, then it is returned."
msgstr ""

